Car_TamweelreqCstm_.Cstm_No LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.tasedwaylist AS Car_Tamweelreqtasedway ON Car_Tamweelreq.tasedwayid = Car_Tamweelreqtasedway.tasedwayid LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.Fuellevel AS Fuel ON LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.masngerclass AS Slm_masngerclass ON Slm_.masngerclassid = Slm_masngerclass.masngerclassid LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.typecolist AS typco ON ajrContracts.typcoid = typco.typcoid LEFT OUTER usingcodsgm ON usingcod.sgm = usingcodsgm.sgm LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.PYCntry AS usingcodCntry_ ON usingcod.Cntry_No = usingcodCntry_.Cntry_No LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.Stcurncy AS usingcodcurncy_ ON
